  <span id="freeText18009840731988117099" style="display:none">This second book in the series held my interest, but I don't think it was as good as the first. Typical?<br /><br />There was a higher level of cruelty and depravity in this book. I like Carl, Assad, and the addition of Rose. I had hoped to learn more about Assad, but not from this book. I'm curious to see where the next books go with these characters.</span>
